boss_descirbe: Enemies' Active Skills deal 10 hits of high DMG based on their Max HP.
The enemies have extremely high DMG Reflection, reflecting DMG back to the attacker. Therefore, discretion is advised when choosing attack means and timing.
Enemies take reduced DMG from Revelation Skills and Creatorâ€™s Will, making more advanced forms of attack less effective against them.
Enemies can inflict Debuffs greatly lowering ATK, making DMG output more difficult.
Whenever the enemies act, they can generate and stack strong Shield for themselves.
After an enemy acts, they will lock on a column and deal 10 hits of high DMG.
Enemies will greatly lower the Buff effectiveness of their opponents.
